  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 3rd level, you may spend a bonus action to activate your <strong>Tatarigan</strong>, for the next minute or until you fall unconscious, whichever happen first. while your Tatarigan is active, you gain chakra sight up to 60ft, in addition, creatures that you can see within your Tatarigan's range gain a -1 penalty to saving throws against genjutsu you cast that do not deal damage, and Fujou clan Hijutsu, once per casting. You can deactivate your Tatarigan as a bonus action on your turn.</p><p>At 7th level, the curses of your eyes grow more powerful, and the penalty to saving throws becomes -2. This becomes -3 at 15th level.</p><p>Starting at 11th level, your spirit vision expands, giving you 90ft of chakra sight and truesight. This becomes 120ft at 18th level.</p>",
